			<div class="container">
				<h1 class="entry-title">Animatronic Head Kit for micro:bit</h1>			</div>
		</div>

		
		<div id="content-inside" class="container right-sidebar">
			<div id="primary" class="content-area">
				<main id="main" class="site-main" role="main">

					
						
<article id="post-1901" class="post-1901 page type-page status-publish hentry">
	<header class="entry-header">
			</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Buy: <a href="https://coolcomponents.co.uk/products/animatronic-head-kit-for-micro-bit"><img data-attachment-id="2097" data-permalink="https://www.monkmakes.com/mb_head/cool_components/" data-orig-file="https://www.monkmakes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/cool_components.png" data-orig-size="268,73" data-comments-opened="0" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="cool_components" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://www.monkmakes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/cool_components.png" data-large-file="https://www.monkmakes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/cool_components.png" class="alignnone wp-image-2097" src="https://www.monkmakes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/cool_components.png" alt="" width="150" height="41" /></a></p>
<p>This kit provides everything you need (apart from a micro:bit and batteries) to make a talking animatronic head. Its eyes move and the head speaks from a MonkMakes Speaker for micro:bit.</p>
<p><img data-attachment-id="2083" data-permalink="https://www.monkmakes.com/mb_head/olympus-digital-camera-55/" data-orig-file="https://www.monkmakes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/finished_main.jpg" data-orig-size="1774,1818" data-comments-opened="0" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;20&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;E-M10MarkII&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;OLYMPUS DIGITAL CAMERA&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1565693717&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;22&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;200&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.1&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;OLYMPUS DIGITAL CAMERA&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="OLYMPUS DIGITAL CAMERA" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://www.monkmakes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/finished_main-293x300.jpg" data-large-file="https://www.monkmakes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/finished_main-999x1024.jpg" class="size-medium wp-image-2083" src="https://www.monkmakes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/finished_main-293x300.jpg" alt="" width="293" height="300" srcset="https://www.monkmakes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/finished_main-293x300.jpg 293w, https://www.monkmakes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/finished_main-768x787.jpg 768w, https://www.monkmakes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/finished_main-999x1024.jpg 999w" sizes="(max-width: 293px) 100vw, 293px" /></p>
<h2>Instructions</h2>
<p>The kit comes with a 30 page printed color booklet. You can also <a href="/downloads/mb_anim_instructions.pdf">download an electronic copy here</a>.</p>
<h2>Software</h2>
<p>The programs for this project are a mixture of Makecode blocks and MicroPython. MicroPython is needed for some projects as the speech module is not available as blocks code and its nice to have the robot talk.</p>
<h3>Program 0. Eyes Front</h3>
